                 <p>
                  <img alt="" class="img-responsive" src="/Portals/0/willkommen.JPG" style="width: 278px; height: 46px; float: left;"/>
                 </p>
                 <p>
                 </p>
                 <p>
                 </p>
                 <p>
                  <span style="color: rgb(102, 102, 102);">
                   <img alt="" class="img-responsive" src="/Portals/0/HomepageFront.jpg" style="width: 350px; height: 184px; float: right;"/>
                  </span>
                 </p>
                 <p>
                  <span style="color: rgb(102, 102, 102);">
                   Die Stadtbibliothek Reinbek bietet Ihnen rund 40.000 Medien zur Ausleihe an. Darunter befinden sich Romane und Sachbücher, Zeitschriften, DVDs,  Hörbücher und Hörspiele für Kinder und Erwachsene.
                  </span>
                 </p>
                 <p>
                  <span style="color: rgb(102, 102, 102);">
                   Außerdem verfügen wir über besondere Angebote für Kitas und Schulen sowie für Senioren und Migranten. Über die Büchereizentrale Schleswig-Holstein sind wir mit anderen Bibliotheken vernetzt und können Ihnen auch von dort Medien bestellen. Außerdem stellt die Stadtbibliothek allen Besuchern ein kostenloses WLAN-Netz zur Verfügung.
                  </span>
                 </p>

                    function dnn_ctr468_View_Html5ContentCanvasCheckCoverImg(selector) {
 		$("<img/>").attr("src", $(selector).attr("src")).load(function () {
 			if (this.width === 1)
 				dnn_ctr468_View_Html5ContentCanvasSetNextCover(selector);
 			else {
 				dnn_ctr468_View_Html5ContentCanvasReloadHtml5ContentModuleCanvas();
 			}
 		});
 	}
 
 	function dnn_ctr468_View_Html5ContentCanvasSetSimpleCover(src, url, srcselector) {
 		srcselector.attr('src', src);
 	}
 
 	function dnn_ctr468_View_Html5ContentCanvasSetNoCover(src, url, srcselector) {
 		srcselector.removeAttr('onerror').removeAttr('onload').attr('src', src);
 		dnn_ctr468_View_Html5ContentCanvasReloadHtml5ContentModuleCanvas();
 	}
 
 	function dnn_ctr468_View_Html5ContentCanvasSetCoverByAjax(url, data, srcselector) {
 		$.ajax({
 			type: "POST",
 			url: url,
 			contentType: "application/json;charset=utf-8",
 			dataType: "json",
 			data: "{'data':'" + data + "'}",
 			success: function (returndata) {
 				if (returndata.d.CoverUrl) {
 					srcselector.attr('src', returndata.d.CoverUrl);
 				}
 				else dnn_ctr468_View_Html5ContentCanvasSetNextCover(srcselector);
 			}
 		});
 	}
 
 	function dnn_ctr468_View_Html5ContentCanvasSetNextCover(selector) {
 		var arr = selector.attr('sources').split('|c|');
 		if (arr.length > 0) {
 			var command = arr.shift();
 			selector.attr('sources', arr.join('|c|'));
 			if (command.length > 0) {
 				var commandarr = command.split('|a|');
 				var meth = commandarr[0];
 				var arg1 = commandarr[1];
 				var arg2 = commandarr[2];
 				window['dnn_ctr468_View_Html5ContentCanvas'+meth](arg1, arg2, selector, selector.parent());
 			}
 		}
 	}
 
 	function dnn_ctr468_View_Html5ContentCanvasReloadHtml5ContentModuleCanvas() {
 		$('#dnn_ctr468_View_Html5ContentCanvas').tagcanvas("reload");
 	}
 
 	function dnn_ctr468_View_Html5ContentCanvasCheckLinksToDisplay() {
 		if ($('#dnn_ctr468_View_Html5ContentTags').find('a').length == 0) {
 			$('#dnn_ctr468_View_Html5ContentCanvasContainer').hide();
 			$('#dnn_ctr468_View_Html5ContentTags').hide();
 			$('#dnn_ctr468_View_Html5ContentNoLinks').show();
 			return false;
 		}
 		return true;
 	}

 		if (dnn_ctr468_View_Html5ContentCanvasCheckLinksToDisplay())
 			if (!$('#dnn_ctr468_View_Html5ContentCanvas').tagcanvas({
 				shape: 'vring(0)',
 				initial: [0.03, 0],
 				offsetY: 0,
 				radiusX: 1,
 				radiusY: 1,
 				radiusZ: 1,
 				minBrightness: 1,
 				lock: 'y',
 				shadow: 'gray',
 				shadowOffset: [0, 0],
 				shadowBlur: 5,
 				tooltip: 'div',
 				tooltipClass: 'dnn_ctr468_View_Html5ContentCanvasTctooltip',
 				tooltipDelay: 0,
 				outlineMethod: 'block',
 				outlineRadius: 0,

 				stretchX: 3,
 				hideTags: true,

 			}, 'dnn_ctr468_View_Html5ContentTags')) {
 				// something went wrong, hide the canvas container
 				$('#dnn_ctr468_View_Html5ContentCanvasContainer').hide();
 				dnn_ctr468_View_Html5ContentCanvasMakeTooltip();
 			}
 
 		$('#dnn_ctr468_View_Html5ContentCanvas').mouseleave(function() {
 			$(this).tagcanvas("setspeed", [0.03, 0]);
 		});
 	}
 
 	function dnn_ctr468_View_Html5ContentCanvasActivateHtml5ContentModuleCanvasWordCloud() {
 		if (dnn_ctr468_View_Html5ContentCanvasCheckLinksToDisplay())
 			if (!$('#dnn_ctr468_View_Html5ContentCanvas').tagcanvas({

 				outlineThickness: 1,
